IMAPAccount shilling.jake
Host imap.gmail.com
User shilling.jake@gmail.com
Timeout 0
PassCmd "pass mail/shilling.jake@gmail.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

# remote storage (use the imap account specified above)
IMAPStore shilling.jake-remote
Account shilling.jake

# local storage
MaildirStore shilling.jake-local
Path ~/.mail/shilling.jake/
Inbox ~/.mail/shilling.jake/Inbox
Subfolders Verbatim

# channel to remote storage
Channel shilling.jake
Far :shilling.jake-remote:
Near :shilling.jake-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
SyncState *
